Birch / audit

This article is about an HIV infected person with a new coronavirus who, after being cured, pays tribute to his partner, who is also infected with HIV and infected with COVID-19. His partner, COVID-19, died on February 6. He was quarantined only after the death of his partner and was diagnosed with a new infection on February 22. He was recently discharged from Vulcan Mountain Hospital. In his mind, it was his partner who traded his life for his life. Fate can be cruel sometimes, but we must learn to face it and choose to live well in the end.

The deceased patient was also the latest case of death of an HIV infected person due to new coronavirus infection, according to the Bai Hualin National Union, on behalf of the Birchwood National Union and our fellow patients, we would like to express our condolences to the deceased and his family.

The basic condition of the deceased a friend infected with the new crown is: a 56-year-old male from Wuhan, who had not combined with other diseases, had been taking the Zillah combination, the disease load could not be detected, more than CD4-500. Anti-virus treatment of AIDS is relatively stable. He developed a fever on January 22,2020, and went to the hospital on January 23,2020, where he was admitted. However, due to the large number of patients at that time, he was not able to be admitted to the hospital for treatment of the new crown until his death. Unfortunately, he died on February 6,2020.

That winter,

- In memory of my friend

I will never forget the winter of early 2020, when I lost the one I loved most, the one who stood by me, who helped me, who helped me, who helped me, who helped me, for the last 12 years.

It's killing me. It's the first time I've ever experienced a painful separation.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
February 6,2020, this time it really pricked my heart, I helped him to go to the toilet, he said he couldn't move his legs, and then he collapsed into a coma, I called him, he didn't speak, I tried to carry him to bed, but he couldn't move, i dragged him to the edge of the bed and laid his body on top of mine. I pushed myself and his body onto the bed, and when I finally got him on the bed, I called out to him. He opened his eyes, and his lips turned blue, and he looked at me.

It was the last time he looked at me before he died. Then he closed his eyes again. I kept calling him 120,110. I screamed his name, I cried, I tried to wake him up, but he didn't respond, i will never forget the sight that shook my heart. The person closest to me left me, but I couldn't save him.

I stayed by his side at two in the morning, wiped him clean and touched his cold body, hoping that he was only asleep, and the next morning I could greet him as usual, but the dawn did not take away his cold body, i took the one I loved.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
No one can help me now that he's gone. I'm the only one left to deal with this. Including the day to give him a death certificate, contact the funeral home, all I ran alone, I really feel too bad, no one can help me, no one in the scene to comfort me, these let me still can not get out of the shadow.

It was like the end of the world, just him and me. And he's gone, leaving me to face the unknown.

I'm not afraid of infection, I just hope he can get better soon, I go with him every day to get an injection, take care of him, make him something he likes to eat, buy him the strawberries and cherubs he wants to eat, then I'll feel safe watching him eat them all, and sleep with him.

He had a fever for 8 days, and I watched his temperature every day to see if it had come down, and for 4 days he had a fever of 38 or more. He took fever medicine for 4 days, and every night he sweated several times. I dried him off, changed his wet clothes and put on clean clothes. I thought the fever was gone, that it would get better. But the last two days chest and back pain, systemic pain, a few times to seek medical admission, and finally in no bed, can not be treated in time to leave me.

I'm not afraid to die. If he lives, I'd rather die in his place, but I can't save him.

I blame myself and regret it all the time. I didn't choose the right option. I didn't let him get away with it.

I told him many times, find another hospital to find out what's wrong, he won't go.

Two hours before he died, he had vomited up all his evening food, his face was Pale and bloodless, and I reminded him once again that he had to be taken to the hospital, where he could always call a doctor if anything went wrong, but he didn't go.

I should have begged him to go, I did not make the right choice, did not take care of him, so I still regret and self-blame.

Every day I think of him, I will feel bad self-blame, heartache and tears.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
I was alone in the face of his death, repeatedly called 110,120,120 is also 40 minutes to arrive. These are desperate times. If it were normal... He'll be here in 10 minutes. He'll live.

As the undertaker pulled him away, I chased him down the stairs and ran after him, shouting his name. I could not accompany him all the way to the undertaker because of the emergency, and I wept bitterly and bitterly as I watched the hearse go away, i wish he'd stayed with me a little longer.

I have to bury him, I have to raise a family for his son, I have to fulfill his dying wish, I have to bury him in our city, next to my loved ones, I have to condense his photographs and videos from every period on a flash drive, to be buried with him, to see him every year, to be buried with him when I die, to be with him when we are born.

His life is too bitter, think of his life bitter, I shed tears, I really want to replace him to go, let him survive. Why did he leave me here to suffer in this world? I can't get rid of this demon.

I was so helpless, so lonely, and I was the only one left in the world, and I was the only one left to face it. My relative couldn't come because of the isolation of the neighborhood, and his son couldn't come because of the isolation of the neighborhood, and that was too much for me to deal with.

Up to now, when I don't care about it every day, I will think of him when I touch the scene. No one will ask me how I am, tell me how I am, and care for me every day. No one will cut my hair, cut my nails, wash my clothes, and cook a delicious meal, he was a diligent man, a quick worker, he kept his house in good order and clean, he gave me a warm and happy home, we were together for more than 10 years, Inseparable, together with the world, each other to continue the life of the other side, to obtain a higher quality of life, before he was alive all kinds of good to me, at that time accustomed to, did not cherish, now has become an extravagant hope, become a good memory, never to return.

Without Him, I suffer every day in pain, often in tears, sad self-blame, long night I often miss him, shouting his name, tossing difficult sleep, sad.

Now I finally understand the impermanence of the world, the fragility of life, not all things will develop smoothly according to their own wishes, at any time there will be a time when the end of the song, the two people together days are extremely precious, live to cherish the people in front of you, cherish the people you love most now, don't quarrel with the people you love, otherwise with their own lives can not recover him.

Without Him, I have no future, I have thoughts of going with him all the time, I will never forget you, my love who has supported each other for 12 years (September 18,2008-february 6,2020) .

In the next life, we'll be a family, and we'll be together forever.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
I really want to get you to call me again, to hear you want me to come home as soon as possible voice, you want me to eat on time, go to bed early, warm and cold clothes of those care and love, I no longer have

Please come back to me. Don't leave me again.

Where are you, my love.
